AIIMS Delhi Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for Research Assistant/ Project Technical Support III Posts
Harshitha / All Government Jobs / Aug 05, 2025, 14:36 IST
 All India Institute of Medical Science Delhi
 1 Jobs |  Posted On : 05-Aug-2025 |  Delhi |  Salary : 28,000 to 28,000




FOLLOW

The All India Institute of Medical Sciences Delhi  (AIIMS Delhi) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 01 Research Assistant/ Project Technical Support III Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their BDS, MDS can apply for the AIIMS Delhi Recruitment 2025. The interested applicants can apply in online mode. Here we have mentioned the education details, age limit, selection process, application fee, salary, and how to apply for these posts before the deadline. The application dates have already begun.




If you are more interested in Government Jobs, candidates can also apply for jobs in Delhi.

AIIMS Delhi Recruitment 2025 Eligiblity Criteria:
Name of the Posts	Vacancies	Education
Research Assistant/ Project Technical Support III	01	BDS, MDS

AIIMS Delhi Recruitment 2025 Age Limit:

The minimum age limit: 21 Years.
The maximum age limit: 35 Years.
Age relaxation is based on the Organisation's norms.

AIIMS Delhi Recruitment 2025 Selection Process:

The selection process is based on the interview.

AIIMS Delhi Recruitment 2025 Application Fee:

There is no application fee.

AIIMS Delhi Recruitment 2025 Pay Scale:

The basic pay: Rs. 28,000/- per month.
How to Apply for the AIIMS Delhi Recruitment 2025:
Go to the official website.
Visit the AIIMS Delhi Recruitment 2025 notification.
Read the instructions carefully and check the eligiblity criteria.
Fill out the application form without any mistakes.
Pay the application fee (if needed).
Attach the required documents to the filled application form.
Submit the filled application form before the last date.
Download & take a printout of the filled application form for further use.

Important Dates:

Starting date	04-08-2025
Closing date	11-08-2025
